  <div class="post-alt blog" id="post-727">
    <h1>The Dark Side of Chocolate: Healthy or Hype?</h1>
        <div class="singletags">
      Keywords: <a href="http://healthnews.staging.ervana.com/keywords/appetite" rel="tag">appetite</a>, <a href="http://healthnews.staging.ervana.com/keywords/cake" rel="tag">cake</a>, <a href="http://healthnews.staging.ervana.com/keywords/chocolate" rel="tag">chocolate</a>, <a href="http://healthnews.staging.ervana.com/keywords/cravings" rel="tag">cravings</a>, <a href="http://healthnews.staging.ervana.com/keywords/diet" rel="tag">diet</a>, <a href="http://healthnews.staging.ervana.com/keywords/nutrition" rel="tag">nutrition</a>, <a href="http://healthnews.staging.ervana.com/keywords/snacks" rel="tag">snacks</a>, <a href="http://healthnews.staging.ervana.com/keywords/weight-loss" rel="tag">weight loss</a>    </div>
        <ul class="main-content-tools">
      <li><a title="Comments on The Dark Side of Chocolate: Healthy or Hype?" href="http://healthnews.staging.ervana.com/health-topics/the-dark-side-of-chocolate-healthy-or-hype.html#discuss">Add Comment</a> </li>
